                <note place="mTop" hand="https://edition-humboldt.de/H0012069 http://d-nb.info/gnd/118554700"><pb n="1v" facs="http://content.staatsbibliothek-berlin.de/dms/PPN838243568/1200/0/00000002.jpg"/><p>fruit Javanais <lb/><hi rendition="#u">polo</hi>. <lb/><unclear reason="illegible" cert="low">Abdallith</unclear></p>
